35/* SunATM header for ATM packet */
36#define SUNATM_DIR_POS 0
37#define SUNATM_VPI_POS 1
38#define SUNATM_VCI_POS 2
39#define SUNATM_PKT_BEGIN_POS 4 /* Start of ATM packet */
40
41/* Protocol type values in the bottom for bits of the byte at SUNATM_DIR_POS. */
42#define PT_LANE 0x01 /* LANE */
43#define PT_LLC 0x02 /* LLC encapsulation */
44#define PT_ILMI 0x05 /* ILMI */
45#define PT_QSAAL 0x06 /* Q.SAAL */
46
